original_title: Salute to Apollo: EAA AirVenture Oshkosh 2017
overview: In this video, you can hear their stories in their own words. David Hartman hosts a Salute to the Apollo Program featuring astronauts Walt Cunningham, Frank Borman, Jim Lovell, Buzz Aldrin, Dick Gordon, Fred Haise, Al Worden, Jack Schmitt, Joe Engle, and flight director Gene Kranz.
title: Salute to Apollo: EAA AirVenture Oshkosh 2017
